comments: Both Tillman (MEM) and Jokic (DEN) come together at the top of the key, and marginal contact occurs prior to Jokic establishing himself in a position to set the pick.
Jokic's (DEN) shot attempt does not make contact with the rim as time expires on the shot clock.
After the hand-off, Jokic (DEN) turns to roll to the basket, causing marginal contact to occur with Williams (MEM).
Porter Jr.'s (DEN) right hand dislodges the ball while his left simultaneously causes marginal contact to occur with Tillman (MEM) during the rebound.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) grabs Tillman's (MEM) off-arm during the drive, affecting his SQBR.
Tillman (MEM) establishes himself in Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Tillman (MEM) establishes himself in Murray's (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Gordon's (DEN) right foot is on the baseline when he receives the pass.
Gordon (DEN) moves alongside Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he absorbs the body contact during the driving shot attempt.
Tillman (MEM) pursues the rebound, and marginal contact occurs to Jokic's (DEN) arm as he makes the controlled tip pass to his teammate Murray (DEN).
Tillman (MEM) commits a take foul on Jokic (DEN).
Tillman (MEM) commits a take foul on Jokic (DEN).
Jokic (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball last before it goes out of bounds. MEM maintains possession of the ball.
Porter Jr. (DEN) legally contests Bane's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
